data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Dunnavant Square neighborhood. This immaculately maintained residence, offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort. Across from Mt. Laurel, this location provides you with access to shops and restaurants, all within walking distance or a quick golf cart ride away. With 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, this beautiful home offers ample space. The main level features the master-suite, a formal dining room, open concept living room with a spacious kitchen and a cozy breakfast nook. From the kitchen, step out onto the inviting covered patio, where you can enjoy outdoor living. You also have have a drop zone by the garage entrance. As you ascend to the upper level, you'll discover two bonus spaces. The first is to your left as you reach the top of the stairs. The second bonus space is strategically positioned between the 3 additional bedrooms and 2 more full bathroom. This home is a true embodiment of quality living in a prime location.
